        {
          "severity": "emergency",
          "criteria": "incarceration, obstruction, strangulation",
          "treatment": "Emergency surgery. Open or laparoscopic exploration. Assess bowel viability. Resection if non-viable. Repair with primary suturing if contaminated, mesh if clean."
